<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV113">
<l>calaṅkalanta ceñcaṭaikka ṟuttakaṇṭaṉ veṇṭalaip</l>
<l>pulaṉkalaṅka vuṇṭapāta kattaṉvaṉtu yarkeṭa</l>
<l>alaṅkaṉmārvil vācanīrko ṭuttavaṉa ṭuttacīr</l>
<l>nalaṅkoṇmālai naṇṇumvaṇṇa meṇṇuvāḻi neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart! May you prosper! Think of</l>
<l rend="indent">the excellence of Him who gave the fragrant water from [His] garlanded chest</l>
<l rend="indent">To destroy the mighty distress of [Śiva with the] grievous sin—</l>
<l rend="indent">he with red matted locks mixed with the waters [of the Ganges],</l>
<l rend="indent">the black-throated one, who ate from the white skull</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the sense organs were confused—</l>
<l>In such a way that [you] approach the good Māl!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
